<div class="map">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <h1 class="map__header">Learn about our <a href="">journey</a></h1>
        <h2 class="map__subheader">You can start with seeing our overall backpacking journey. See what route we took, the countries we visited, and why!</h2>
        <button class="button button__ghost">Our Journey</button>
        <h3 class="map__subheader"> More interested in a specific country? Click below to take a look</h3>
        <div class="map__container">
            <div class="map__descriptions">
                <div class="map__descriptions--row">
                    <div class="map__country">
                        <a href="#"><img data-src="assets/images/homepage/colombia-home-edited.jpg" alt="Colombia quick access" class="lazyload map__descriptions-picture"></a>
                        <div class="map__list">
                            <a href=""><h2>Incredibly friendly people with untouched natural beauty</h2></a>
                            <p>The days of Escobar are over. Colombia is safe and stunning! There's so much to see and do here. Thomas' favourite country!</p>
                            <p class="map__highlight-intro">Some quick highlights</p>
                            <ul class="map__quick-highlights">
                                <a href=""><li>Santa Marta - Home to the worlds largest hammock and scuba diving</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Salento - The coffee region, and one of our coolest stays</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Medellin - Once the worlds most dangerous city was recently voted the most innovative</a>

                            </ul>
                        </div>
                       
                    </div>

                   <div class="map__country">
                        <a href="#"><img data-src="assets/images/homepage/ecuador-home.jpg" alt="Ecuador quick access" class="lazyload map__descriptions-picture"></a>
                        <div class="map__list">
                            <a href=""><h2>A beautiful country with special little islands</h2></a>
                            <p>We could go on and on about the Galapagos, and we will. There's no place else like it, full of lively wildlife and endemic animals. Oh, the mainland is cool too.</p>
                            <p class="map__highlight-intro">Some quick highlights</p>
                            <ul class="map__quick-highlights">
                                <a href=""><li>Galapagos Islands - Ever worry things things get overhyped? Galaps are not one</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Quito - See the middle of the world, and enjoy the city's history</li></a>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="map__country">
                        <a href="#"><img data-src="assets/images/homepage/peru-home.jpg" alt="Peru quick access" class="lazyload map__descriptions-picture"></a>
                        <div class="map__list">
                            <a href=""><h2>From rainforests to mountains to deserts and beaches</h2></a>
                            <p>There's so much adventure waiting in Peru for all types of people. There's also this mountain called Macchu Picchu, heard of it?</p>
                            <p class="map__highlight-intro">Some quick highlightss</p>
                            <ul class="map__quick-highlights">
                                <a href=""><li>Hauraz - a climbers dream. Breath taking mountains and trails</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Cusco and Machu Picchu - You know what it is. One of our top adventures</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Huacachina - Learn to sandboard at the desert oasis</li></a>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="map__country">
                        <a href="#"><img data-src="assets/images/homepage/bolivia-home3.jpg" alt="Bolivia quick access" class="lazyload map__descriptions-picture"></a>
                        <div class="map__list">
                            <a href=""><h2>Some of the most jaw-dropping landscapes</h2></a>
                            <p>A highly underrated country with the coolest national park we've ever seen. Get ready for cool perspective pictures!</p>
                            <p class="map__highlight-intro">Some quick highlights</p>
                            <ul class="map__quick-highlights">
                                <a href=""><li>Sucre - The real capital of Bolivia. A hidden gem of a city</li></a>
                                <a href=""><li>Salt Flats - Explore the salt flats and the massive National Park</li></a>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div> 
                </div>  
            </div>
